des:
"The Broan-NuTone voice control helps end users control their bathroom ventilation voice easily. You can simply ask Alexa to control your fan, light, etc. after connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:

1. Download our VoiceControl app in app market and register an account;

2. Configure your devices in our VoiceControl app and choose appropriate name for your devices;

3. Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android, iOS or Amazon app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;

4. Search “Broan-NuTone Voice Control” skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;

5. Enable “Broan-NuTone Voice Control” skill, and you'll be navigated to the “Broan-NuTone Voice Control” login page;

6. Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;

7. Now the setup is finished. You can enjoy voice control on your bath fan with commands like these:

Alexa, turn on fan;

Alexa, turn off fan;

Alexa, turn on light;

Alexa, turn off light;

Alexa, turn the light on to the daylight setting;

Alexa turn the brightness down 50%.”
